me.lucko.helper.metadata

Interface MetadataKey<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the value type
    All Superinterfaces:
    TypeAware<T>

    @NonnullByDefault
public interface MetadataKey<T>
extends TypeAware<T>
    A MetadataKey can be mapped to values in a MetadataMap.

    Unlike a normal map key, a MetadataKey also holds the type of the values mapped to it.
